### Get simple select

POST http://localhost:8080/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "SELECT 1"
}

### Get all tables

POST http://localhost:8080/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "SELECT * from system.tables;"
}

### Multi-statement script (split + sequential run, shared session)

POST http://localhost:8080/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS test_table (id UInt32) ENGINE = Memory;\nINSERT INTO test_table VALUES (1), (2);\nSELECT * FROM test_table"
}

### Upload SQL file (multipart field name: file, max 2 MB, .sql / .txt only)

POST http://localhost:8080/query/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="script.sql"
Content-Type: application/sql

SELECT 1 AS uploaded
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
